               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>ELIZABETH WILD <rs id="t17761016-41-verdict244" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17761016-41-verdict244" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron EYRE.</p>
